{"type":"message","id":"89b7d150","parentId":"606d761d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:37:08.862Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ByyuDS8yO5lIlZohsM5obdY5|fc_07578b46fd5875bf0169b218bb74c8819180831d5c5f7b0c1f","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[vrchat-relay] Registering VRChat Relay plugin (Pro Edition)...\n[vrchat-relay] VRChat Relay Pro plugin registered successfully\n[vrchat-relay] Features: Camera Control, Permission Profiles, Rate Limiting, OSCQuery Discovery\nChecking channel status (probe)…\nGateway not reachable; showing config-only status.\nConfig: C:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nMode: local\n\n- Telegram default: enabled, configured, mode:polling, token:env\n- Discord default: enabled, configured, token:env\n- Slack default: enabled, not configured, bot:env\n- LINE default: enabled, configured, mode:webhook, token:config\n\nTip: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli#status adds gateway health probes to status output (requires a reachable gateway).\ngateway connect failed: Error: EPERM: operation not permitted, open 'C:\\Users\\downl\\Desktop\\clawdbot-main3\\clawdbot-main\\.openclaw-desktop\\identity\\device-auth.json'\nGateway not reachable: Error: gateway closed (1008): connect failed\nGateway target: http://127.0.0.1:18789\nSource: env OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL\nConfig: C:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"clear-fjord","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[vrchat-relay] Registering VRChat Relay plugin (Pro Edition)...\n[vrchat-relay] VRChat Relay Pro plugin registered successfully\n[vrchat-relay] Features: Camera Control, Permission Profiles, Rate Limiting, OSCQuery Discovery\nChecking channel status (probe)…\ngateway connect failed: Error: EPERM: operation not permitted, open 'C:\\Users\\downl\\Desktop\\clawdbot-main3\\clawdbot-main\\.openclaw-desktop\\identity\\device-auth.json'\nGateway not reachable: Error: gateway closed (1008): connect failed\nGateway target: http://127.0.0.1:18789\nSource: env OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_URL\nConfig: C:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nGateway not reachable; showing config-only status.\nConfig: C:\\Users\\downl\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\nMode: local\n\n- Telegram default: enabled, configured, mode:polling, token:env\n- Discord default: enabled, configured, token:env\n- Slack default: enabled, not configured, bot:env\n- LINE default: enabled, configured, mode:webhook, token:config\n\nTip: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli#status adds gateway health probes to status output (requires a reachable gateway).\n","name":"$cli='C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd'; &"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773279428854}}
{"type":"message","id":"2132a6e5","parentId":"89b7d150","timestamp":"2026-03-12T01:37:19.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 特定できたよ。\n\n- インストール実体: `C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd`\n- たぶん PATH に入っていないのは: `C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm`\n\nLINE チャネル状態は現状こう:\n- `LINE default: enabled, configured, mode:webhook, token:config`\n\nただし詳細プローブは失敗してる:\n- Gateway not reachable\n- 接続先: `http://127.0.0.1:18789`\n- 追加エラー:  \n  `EPERM: operation not permitted, open 'C:\\Users\\downl\\Desktop\\clawdbot-main3\\clawdbot-main\\.openclaw-desktop\\identity\\device-auth.json'`\n\n要するに、\n1. LINE 設定自体は入ってる  \n2. でも Gateway に繋がってないので稼働確認まではできてない  \n3. さらに `device-auth.json` まわりの権限/ファイルアクセス問題もある\n\n今すぐやるならこの順がよさそう:\n1. PATH 修正  \n   PowerShell なら一時的に:\n   ```powershell\n   $env:Path += \";C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\"\n   ```\n   永続化するならユーザー PATH に\n   `C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm`\n   を追加\n\n2. Gateway 状態確認\n   ```powershell\n   C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd gateway status\n   ```\n\n3. 必要なら起動\n   ```powershell\n   C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd gateway start\n   ```\n\n4. その後もう一度\n   ```powershell\n   C:\\Users\\downl\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd channels status --probe\n   ```\n\n必要なら次に、\n- PATH を永続修正するコマンド\n- `device-auth.json` の EPERM 切り分け\n- LINE が実際に webhook 受信できるかの確認\n\nまで続けてやるよ。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07578b46fd5875bf0169b218ca2d888191a72f24efaf71c1b1\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":418,"output":510,"cacheRead":18176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19104,"cost":{"input":0.0010450000000000001,"output":0.0076500000000000005,"cacheRead":0.004543999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013239}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773279428860}}
